static fake_ci_t(X, Y, Z=[], **kwargs)[source]

A mock CI testing function which gives False for every condition except for the following:

  1. B ⟂ C

  2. B ⟂ D

  3. C ⟂ D

  4. A ⟂ B | C

  5. A ⟂ C | B
